        <abstract>
            <p>CD thanks JJW for the mine of information his last "ten!" letters contain. Comments on sexual display of pheasants and colour preferences of pigeons.</p>
            <p>Asks about hens that pair earliest in spring and about possible existence of unpaired birds.</p>
